* Install vagrant
* Create a directory somewhere for working on the code:

mkdir /some/path

* check out the code:

cd /some/path
git clone <git URL>
cd syllabalastic
git submodule init
git submodule update --recursive

* Put vagranty things in place:

cp vagrant_config/* ../

* Spin up a VM:

vagrant up --provision

* Browse to http://localhost:3456 and fiddle.
